Package: bananarama
Title: Generate Presentation Images Using Google Gemini
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hadley", "Wickham", , "hadley@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Reproducibly generate slide images using Google Gemini.
    Define your images in a YAML configuration file with support for
    reference images and style defaults, eliminating the need to copy and
    paste prompts back and forth from a web UI. Images are generated in
    parallel for speed.
